{
  "texts": [
    "Individual tools were mapped to more than one category if they exhibited functions for more than one.",
    "We now provide the definitions for the eight tool categories.",
    "Viral vector design: AI tools for engineering and optimising viral vectors.",
    "We define viral vector design tools to be AI models that enable the engineering and optimisation of viral vectors.",
    "These are commonly applied to adeno-associated viruses (AAVs) for gene therapy applications."
  ]
}